title: 10 Takeaways from Week 12
itunes:title: 10 Takeaways from Week 12
description:
DJ and Bucky discuss Joey Bosa’s immediate impact (0:45), Lamar Jackson making the Ravens a much better offense (3:40), Vikings big win over the Packers (5:35), Seahawks creeping back into contention (9:00), Josh Allen’s formula for success (12:50), Mayfield and the Browns are on the right track (15:30), Eric Ebron shining in the Colts offense (19:05), Bucs shouldn’t give up on Jameis Winston (22:22), Broncos strategy for defending the Steelers (25:30), Sony Michel making an impact with the Pats offense (32:05).
